# Parent declares two independent parameters; the overlay turns them into a
# cycle by retargeting `x`'s RHS so it depends on `y`, which already depends
# on `x`. The cross-instance SCC pass in
# `oneil_analysis::validate_instance_graph` runs over the composed graph
# (post-design) and emits one `ParameterCycle` diagnostic per cycle member.
First: x = 1
Second: y = 2 * x
